description: Professional architectural blueprint for a 1200 Square Meters house with For a 3 BHK house on a 1,200 sq. meter plot in New Delhi with a budget of 20,00,000, the floor plan should include 3 bedrooms (1 master with attached bath), 2 common bathrooms, a living room, dining area, kitchen, and a small utility space. Prioritize natural light and ventilation. Include space for a parking area, garden, and possibly a terrace or balcony. Use cost-effective, local materials and simple design to stay within budget. The layout should be compact, functional, and suitable for a family of 4–6, with provisions for future expansion if needed.. Top-down 2D floor plan with precise measurements, clean lines, labeled rooms, doors, windows, and dimensions. Technical architectural drawing style with blue lines on white background.
